# From: Christopher Swingley <cswingle@iarc.uaf.edu>
<userdetail "UOA-IARC" "Alaska universitet i Fairbanks, IARC &ndash; <span lang='en'>Frontier Program</span>" "http://www.frontier.iarc.uaf.edu">
